A '''critical lens essay''' is a type of analytical [[essay]] that focuses on a [[quotation]] from a piece of literature. The essay states whether the quotation is valid, and explains why using [[literary device]]s. It is an analysis of the quote and uses literary elements and techniques to do so.<ref>{{cite web | title=What Is a Critical Lens Essay? | url=http://www.wisegeek.com/what-is-a-critical-lens-essay.htm | accessdate=2014-03-21 }}</ref>

